# AtomicBool in std::sync::atomic - Rust

```
#[repr(C, align(1))]pub struct AtomicBool { /* private fields */ }
```

Expand description

A boolean type which can be safely shared between threads.

This type has the same size, alignment, and bit validity as a [`bool`](../../primitive.bool.html "primitive bool").

**Note**: This type is only available on platforms that support atomic loads and stores of `u8`.

